org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr
Interface IAeExpressionValidationResult

All Known Implementing Classes:
AeExpressionValidationResult
public interface IAeExpressionValidationResult

An instance of this interface is returned by expression validators. This result includes a list of error messages, if any, as well as a list of AeVariableData and AeVariableProperty objects used by the expression.

public java.util.List getInfoList()
Returns list of information (INFO) messages found during parsing. This method should never return null. In cases where there are no errors, an empty list should be returned.
